judges.name: NAGARAJ HEGADE
judges.description: Shri Nagaraj Hegde, a highly accomplished tabla and harmonium artist, has trained under esteemed gurus and performed alongside renowned musicians across India. Founder of Ghe Tak Sangeet Vidyalaya, he has received numerous accolades, including the Karnataka Sangeeta Kalaratna State Award in 2022.

judges.name: ASHA BADRINATH
judges.description: Asha Badrinath, a seasoned Carnatic vocalist and senior-grade artist in Karnataka Shastriya Sangeet and Ghamak, has performed widely and appeared on major TV channels. As the founder of Guru Raghavendra Sangeet Shaale, she passionately nurtures young talent in classical music.

judges.name: Mrs. VEENA
judges.description: Mrs. Veena, a beauty and fashion expert with 28+ years of experience, excels in makeup artistry, hairstyling, and couture design for weddings and high-fashion events. With a deep passion for aesthetics and innovation, she empowers creativity while redefining beauty and style.

judges.name: Mrs. SRIKANTHI REDDY
judges.description: Mrs. Srikanthi Reddy, a fashion and beauty expert with 18 years of experience in bridal, fashion, and film, specializes in styling, makeup, skincare, and textile design. With a keen eye for detail, she creates personalized, elegant looks that enhance individuality and confidence.
